<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span class="green">不介意，反正我自己也不喜欢<span style="color:black">███</span>这个名字</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span class="blue">那好。我可以问你几个问题吗？</span><br />
